---
// ContactTab.astro
---

<div class="tab-content" id="tab-contact">
      <div class="contact-page">

        <div class="contact-hero">
          <!-- Left: Profile + Links + Booking -->
          <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:14px">
            <div class="contact-lead-copy">
              <h2 class="contact-lead-title" data-pl="Pracujmy razem." data-en="Let's work together." data-it="Lavoriamo insieme.">Let's work together.</h2>
              <p class="contact-lead-body" data-pl="Użyj tego miejsca do aplikacji, GTM, automatyzacji, audytu albo szybkiego review. Podaj cel, stan obecny i linki - odpowiem konkretnie." data-en="Use this for apps, GTM, automation, audits, or a fast review. Share the goal, current state, and links - I will answer with practical next steps." data-it="Usalo per app, GTM, automazioni, audit o review veloci. Condividi obiettivo, stato attuale e link - rispondero con prossimi passi pratici.">Use this for apps, GTM, automation, audits, or a fast review. Share the goal, current state, and links - I will answer with practical next steps.</p>
            </div>
            <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column">
              <a class="cinfo-row" href="mailto:hello@wojciech.io">
                <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8"><rect x="3" y="5" width="18" height="14" rx="2"/><path d="m3 7 9 6 9-6"/></svg>
                <span>hello@wojciech.io</span>
              </a>
              <a class="cinfo-row" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/wojciech-luszczynski/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
                <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M20.447 20.452h-3.554v-5.569c0-1.328-.027-3.037-1.852-3.037-1.853 0-2.136 1.445-2.136 2.939v5.667H9.351V9h3.414v1.561h.046c.477-.9 1.637-1.85 3.37-1.85 3.601 0 4.267 2.37 4.267 5.455v6.286zM5.337 7.433c-1.144 0-2.063-.926-2.063-2.065 0-1.138.92-2.063 2.063-2.063 1.14 0 2.064.925 2.064 2.063 0 1.139-.925 2.065-2.064 2.065zm1.782 13.019H3.555V9h3.564v11.452z"/></svg>
                <span>linkedin.com/in/wojciech-luszczynski</span>
              </a>
            </div>
            <div class="contact-profile-card">
              <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:16px">
                <img class="contact-avatar" src="/wojciech-photo.png">
                <div>
                  <div class="contact-name">Wojciech Łuszczyński</div>
                  <div class="contact-tagline" data-pl="GTM Architect · Builder" data-en="GTM Architect · Builder" data-it="GTM Architect · Builder">GTM Architect · Builder</div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="contact-bio" data-pl="Projektuję i buduję - systemy wzrostu, produkty webowe i AI workflows dla B2B SaaS founderów i scale-upów. Praca zdalna, szybka egzekucja, zero bullshitu." data-en="I design and build - growth systems, web products and AI workflows for B2B SaaS founders and scale-ups. Remote, fast execution, no fluff." data-it="Progetto e costruisco - sistemi di crescita, prodotti web e AI workflow per founder B2B SaaS e scale-up. Lavoro da remoto, esecuzione rapida, zero inutilità.">Projektuję i buduję - systemy wzrostu, produkty webowe i AI workflows dla B2B SaaS founderów i scale-upów. Praca zdalna, szybka egzekucja, zero bullshitu.</div>
            </div>

            <!-- Booking card -->
            <div class="contact-booking-card">
              <div class="contact-avail" style="margin-bottom:14px">
                <span class="contact-avail-dot"></span>
                <span data-pl="Dostępny do nowych projektów" data-en="Available for new projects" data-it="Disponibile per nuovi progetti">Available for new projects</span>
              </div>
              <div style="font-size:15px;font-weight:800;color:var(--text);letter-spacing:-.2px;margin-bottom:4px" data-pl="Umów rozmowę 30 min" data-en="Book a 30-min call" data-it="Prenota una chiamata 30 min">Book a 30-min call</div>
              <div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--text-2);line-height:1.55;margin-bottom:16px" data-pl="Szybka rozmowa o projekcie, współpracy lub review. Bez bullshitu." data-en="Quick chat about a project, collaboration, or review. No fluff." data-it="Breve chat su un progetto, collaborazione o review. Senza fronzoli.">Quick chat about a project, collaboration, or review. No fluff.</div>
              <a href="https://cal.com/wojciech-luszczynski" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="contact-book-btn">
                <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2"/><line x1="16" y1="2" x2="16" y2="6"/><line x1="8" y1="2" x2="8" y2="6"/><line x1="3" y1="10" x2="21" y2="10"/></svg>
                <span data-pl="Zarezerwuj termin" data-en="Schedule a meeting" data-it="Prenota un orario">Schedule a meeting</span>
              </a>
              <div class="contact-links-row" style="margin-top:10px">
                <a href="mailto:hello@wojciech.io" class="contact-link-inline">
                  <svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M4 4h16c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2v12c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2H4c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V6c0-1.1.9-2 2-2z"/><polyline points="22,6 12,13 2,6"/></svg>
                  <span>hello@wojciech.io</span>
                </a>
                <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/wojciech-luszczynski/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="contact-link-inline">
                  <svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M16 8a6 6 0 0 1 6 6v7h-4v-7a2 2 0 0 0-2-2 2 2 0 0 0-2 2v7h-4v-7a6 6 0 0 1 6-6z"></path><rect x="2" y="9" width="4" height="12"></rect><circle cx="4" cy="4" r="2"></circle></svg>
                  <span>LinkedIn</span>
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>

          </div>

          <!-- Right: Form -->
          <div class="contact-form-card">
            <div id="contactFormWrap">
              <div class="contact-intake-head">
                <h3 data-pl="Opisz kontekst operacyjny" data-en="Send the operating context" data-it="Invia il contesto operativo">Send the operating context</h3>
                <p data-pl="Wystarczy cel, obecny stan, najważniejszy blocker i linki. Odpowiem z następnym sensownym krokiem." data-en="Share the goal, current state, main blocker, and useful links. I will reply with the next practical step." data-it="Condividi obiettivo, stato attuale, blocker principale e link utili. Rispondero con il prossimo passo pratico.">Share the goal, current state, main blocker, and useful links. I will reply with the next practical step.</p>
              </div>

              <div class="cf-choice-row" aria-label="Project type">
                <label class="cf-choice">
                  <input type="checkbox" name="projectNeed" value="App / SaaS">
                  <span data-pl="App / SaaS" data-en="App / SaaS" data-it="App / SaaS">App / SaaS</span>
                </label>
                <label class="cf-choice">
                  <input type="checkbox" name="projectNeed" value="Automation">
                  <span data-pl="Automatyzacja" data-en="Automation" data-it="Automazione">Automation</span>
                </label>
                <label class="cf-choice">
                  <input type="checkbox" name="projectNeed" value="Website">
                  <span data-pl="Strona" data-en="Website" data-it="Sito">Website</span>
                </label>
                <label class="cf-choice">
                  <input type="checkbox" name="projectNeed" value="Audit / rescue">
                  <span data-pl="Audit / rescue" data-en="Audit / rescue" data-it="Audit / rescue">Audit / rescue</span>
                </label>
              </div>

              <div class="cf-grid">
                <label class="cf-field">
                  <span class="cf-label" data-pl="Imię" data-en="Name" data-it="Nome">Name</span>
                  <input type="text" class="cf-input" id="intakeName" placeholder="John Smith" autocomplete="name" data-pl-placeholder="Jan Kowalski" data-en-placeholder="John Smith" data-it-placeholder="Mario Rossi">
                </label>
                <label class="cf-field">
                  <span class="cf-label" data-pl="Email" data-en="Email" data-it="Email">Email</span>
                  <input type="email" class="cf-input" id="intakeEmail" placeholder="you@company.com" autocomplete="email" data-pl-placeholder="jan@firma.pl" data-en-placeholder="you@company.com" data-it-placeholder="tu@azienda.it">
                </label>
                <label class="cf-field cf-wide">
                  <span class="cf-label" data-pl="Co trzeba dowieźć?" data-en="What needs to ship?" data-it="Cosa va consegnato?">What needs to ship?</span>
                  <textarea class="cf-input cf-textarea" id="intakeMessage" rows="6" placeholder="Goal, context, deadline, links. Keep it practical." data-pl-placeholder="Cel, kontekst, deadline, linki. Krótko i konkretnie." data-en-placeholder="Goal, context, deadline, links. Keep it practical." data-it-placeholder="Obiettivo, contesto, scadenza, link. Breve e concreto."></textarea>
                </label>
                <label class="cf-field">
                  <span class="cf-label" data-pl="Termin" data-en="Timeline" data-it="Tempistiche">Timeline</span>
                  <select class="cf-input cf-select" id="formTimeline">
                    <option value="" data-pl="Wybierz" data-en="Choose" data-it="Scegli">Choose</option>
                    <option value="ASAP" data-pl="ASAP" data-en="ASAP" data-it="ASAP">ASAP</option>
                    <option value="This month" data-pl="Ten miesiąc" data-en="This month" data-it="Questo mese">This month</option>
                    <option value="This quarter" data-pl="Ten kwartał" data-en="This quarter" data-it="Questo trimestre">This quarter</option>
                    <option value="Exploration" data-pl="Na razie eksploracja" data-en="Exploration" data-it="Esplorazione">Exploration</option>
                  </select>
                </label>
                <label class="cf-field">
                  <span class="cf-label" data-pl="Link / kontekst" data-en="Link / context" data-it="Link / contesto">Link / context</span>
                  <input type="text" class="cf-input" id="formSource" placeholder="Current site, repo, deck, brief..." data-pl-placeholder="Obecna strona, repo, deck, brief..." data-en-placeholder="Current site, repo, deck, brief..." data-it-placeholder="Sito attuale, repo, deck, brief...">
                </label>
              </div>

              <div id="intakeError" class="cf-error" style="display:none"></div>

              <div class="cf-actions">
                <button class="cf-submit-btn" id="intakeSubmitBtn" onclick="cfSubmit()" type="button">
                  <span data-pl="Wyślij wiadomość" data-en="Send message" data-it="Invia messaggio">Send message</span>
                </button>
                <a href="https://cal.com/wojciech-luszczynski" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="cf-secondary-link" data-pl="Albo zarezerwuj call" data-en="Or book a call" data-it="Oppure prenota una call">Or book a call</a>
              </div>

              <div class="cf-meta-row">
                <span data-pl="Odpowiadam zwykle w 24h." data-en="I usually reply within 24h." data-it="Di solito rispondo entro 24h.">I usually reply within 24h.</span>
                <span data-pl="Konkret, potem szybka odpowiedź." data-en="Clear context, fast reply." data-it="Contesto chiaro, risposta rapida.">Clear context, fast reply.</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div id="formSuccess" class="cf-success" style="display:none;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;padding:48px 20px;text-align:center;gap:12px">
              <div style="width:52px;height:52px;border-radius:50%;background:rgba(16,179,108,0.12);border:1px solid rgba(16,179,108,0.28);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center"><svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#10b36c" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline></svg></div>
              <div style="font-size:18px;font-weight:900;color:var(--text)" data-pl="Wysłane. Mam temat." data-en="Sent. I have the context." data-it="Inviato. Ho il contesto.">Wysłane. Mam temat.</div>
              <div style="font-size:13px;color:var(--text-2);max-width:280px;line-height:1.6" data-pl="Odezwę się po przejrzeniu wiadomości. Jeżeli sprawa jest pilna, złap termin w kalendarzu." data-en="I'll reply after reviewing it. If it is urgent, grab a slot in the calendar." data-it="Rispondo dopo averlo letto. Se è urgente, prendi uno slot nel calendario.">Odezwę się po przejrzeniu wiadomości. Jeżeli sprawa jest pilna, złap termin w kalendarzu.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Newsletter band -->
        <div class="nl-band">
          <div class="nl-band-inner">
            <div class="nl-band-left">
              <div class="nl-band-eyebrow" data-pl="Newsletter" data-en="Newsletter" data-it="Newsletter">Newsletter</div>
              <div class="nl-band-title" data-pl="Notatki z budowania systemów." data-en="Build notes from live systems." data-it="Note di build da sistemi reali.">Build notes from live systems.</div>
              <div class="nl-band-sub" data-pl="Krótko: co zbudowałem, dlaczego taki stack, co zadziałało po deployu i co warto powtórzyć." data-en="Short notes on what shipped, why the stack was chosen, what worked after deploy, and what is worth reusing." data-it="Note brevi su cosa e stato rilasciato, perche quello stack, cosa ha funzionato dopo il deploy e cosa riusare.">Short notes on what shipped, why the stack was chosen, what worked after deploy, and what is worth reusing.</div>
              <div class="nl-band-points">
                <div class="nl-band-point" data-pl="Jak buduję produkty AI od zera do deploy'u" data-en="How I build AI products from zero to deployed" data-it="Come costruisco prodotti AI da zero al deploy">How I build AI products from zero to deployed</div>
                <div class="nl-band-point" data-pl="GTM dla produktów technicznych - co działa w 2026" data-en="GTM for technical products - what actually works in 2026" data-it="GTM per prodotti tecnici - cosa funziona davvero nel 2026">GTM for technical products - what actually works in 2026</div>
                <div class="nl-band-point" data-pl="Stack, narzędzia, decyzje architektoniczne bez owijania w bawełnę" data-en="Stack, tools, and architecture decisions without the fluff" data-it="Stack, strumenti e decisioni architetturali senza fronzoli">Stack, tools, and architecture decisions without the fluff</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="nl-band-right">
              <input type="email" class="nl-input" id="nlEmail" data-pl-placeholder="twoj@email.pl" data-en-placeholder="your@email.com" data-it-placeholder="tua@email.it" placeholder="twoj@email.pl">
              <button class="nl-btn" onclick="subscribeNewsletter()"><span data-pl="Zapisz się - za darmo" data-en="Subscribe - it's free" data-it="Iscriviti - è gratis">Subscribe - it's free</span></button>
              <div class="nl-band-note" data-pl="Raz w tygodniu. Wypisz się kiedy chcesz." data-en="Once a week. Unsubscribe anytime." data-it="Una volta a settimana. Cancellati quando vuoi.">Once a week. Unsubscribe anytime.</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div><!-- /contact-page -->
    </div><!-- /tab-contact -->
